      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 11,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Why WAT? -- AI accuracy drops exponentially over chained steps (5 steps @ 90% = 59%).\nOffloading execution to deterministic Python scripts keeps the system reliable.",
